com.sap.cloud.sdk.s4hana.datamodel.odata.services

Interface ProductMasterService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultProductMasterService

    public interface ProductMasterService

    This service enables you to create, read, update, and delete (CRUD operations) the master data for products by exposing the remote API views through OData. This service contains information about product description, plant, sales delivery, storage location, and sales tax.

    Business Documentation

    Reference: SAP API Business Hub

    Details:

    OData Service:API_PRODUCT_SRV
    API Version:1
    Minimum ERP Version:1708
    Communication Scenario:Product Integration (SAP_COM_0009)
    Scope Items:Master Data Integration (1RO)
